snippet.title: v4.5 [Blazing Hope] Trailer - Honkai Impact 3rd
snippet.description:
v4.5 [Blazing Hope] Trailer
The girl from another world finds herself in Nagazora, a city shrouded in the shadow known as "Angel"...

Centering on the [Honkai Impact 3rd x Neon Genesis Evangelion] collab, v4.5 [Blazing Hope] is landing soon! Play the main collab event [New Century] to unlock Asuka's SP battlesuit [Blazing Hope] for free!

Share the trailer to enter the raffle to win a 1/7 Asuka Shikinami Langley Ver.RADIO EVA figure! Limited to 3 winners from all communities of this server regardless of language!

We will announce the winners in the comments on JAN 28!  Stay tuned~

Subscribe our YouTube and turn on notification for latest video : http://bit.ly/HonkaiImpact3rdYTB

https://honkaiimpact3.mihoyo.com/global/
